1
00:01:27,060 --> 00:01:35,980
[Zhan Zhao Adventures]

2
00:01:35,980 --> 00:01:37,980
[Episode 1]

3
00:01:51,980 --> 00:01:56,620
[Shanbei Inn]

4
00:02:16,560 --> 00:02:17,840
Waiter, a pot of wine!

5
00:02:18,030 --> 00:02:18,810
Coming right up!

6
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,390
Innkeeper,

7
00:02:23,930 --> 00:02:24,710
two pots over there.

8
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:25,810
Set them down.

9
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,060
Dahai, stop eating.

10
00:02:48,180 --> 00:02:49,230
We need to get moving.

11
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:50,740
Third Master.

12
00:02:51,380 --> 00:02:52,130
It's pouring out.

13
00:02:52,280 --> 00:02:53,060
What's the rush?

14
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,430
We're moving, storm or not.

15
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,120
We're carrying something important,

16
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,490
better safe than sorry.

17
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,530
Just one last bite.

18
00:02:58,650 --> 00:02:59,490
Let's go after I finish.

19
00:04:16,250 --> 00:04:18,330
Are you Ge Yunfei, the Third Master

20
00:04:18,520 --> 00:04:19,260
of Shengyun Manor?

21
00:04:19,260 --> 00:04:21,580
[Ge Yunfei, Third Master of Shengyun Manor]

22
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:22,730
Leave the item,

23
00:04:22,850 --> 00:04:23,930
and we'll spare you.

24
00:04:24,150 --> 00:04:25,430
You know who I am,

25
00:04:26,250 --> 00:04:27,560
and still dare steal from me?

26
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,090
If you could steal it,

27
00:04:30,180 --> 00:04:31,530
so can we.

28
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,530
You dare cross Shengyun Manor?

29
00:04:36,530 --> 00:04:37,370
You're dead!

30
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:40,400
Dahai!

31
00:04:45,450 --> 00:04:46,060
Tang Clan.

32
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:50,180
[Tang Jiujue, Wuning Hall of the Tang Clan]

33
00:04:54,550 --> 00:04:55,460
Our paths cross!

34
00:06:14,230 --> 00:06:14,780
Watch out!

35
00:06:50,480 --> 00:06:51,330
Are you okay?

36
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,200
You're hurt.

37
00:07:19,350 --> 00:07:20,360
Who did this?

38
00:07:25,150 --> 00:07:26,290
Can't you talk?

39
00:07:27,280 --> 00:07:28,640
But you can hear me,

40
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,220
right?

41
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:36,370
If I find out

42
00:07:36,370 --> 00:07:37,500
who hurt you like this,

43
00:07:38,390 --> 00:07:39,210
I won't let them off.

44
00:07:54,730 --> 00:07:55,780
It seems to like you.

45
00:08:03,260 --> 00:08:03,940
Strange.

46
00:08:04,030 --> 00:08:05,740
That herbal scent on you...

47
00:08:05,930 --> 00:08:07,440
it usually hates that smell.

48
00:08:18,660 --> 00:08:20,210
Everyone from Shengyun Manor is dead.

49
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:21,710
How are you getting back?

50
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:25,000
You're not from Shengyun Manor?

51
00:08:27,530 --> 00:08:28,170
How about this?

52
00:08:28,760 --> 00:08:30,340
Xiangyang is closest from here.

53
00:08:30,530 --> 00:08:31,910
I'll have someone take you there,

54
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:33,140
then we'll inform the authorities.

55
00:08:36,030 --> 00:08:36,810
Innkeeper.

56
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,580
They're back again!

57
00:08:49,950 --> 00:08:50,980
Why are you back?

58
00:08:52,530 --> 00:08:53,980
The item must be on that kid.

59
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:54,510
Search him.

60
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:57,040
Are you blind?

61
00:08:57,160 --> 00:08:58,510
He's barely dressed.

62
00:08:58,600 --> 00:08:59,540
Where could he hide anything?

63
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:00,710
It's not on him,

64
00:09:00,960 --> 00:09:02,040
then it's on you.

65
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,610
Nice Cushion Palm technique.

66
00:09:13,790 --> 00:09:15,010
Hit me if you want,

67
00:09:15,130 --> 00:09:15,840
but bullying

68
00:09:15,840 --> 00:09:16,900
a defenseless kid?

69
00:09:16,900 --> 00:09:18,300
This really ruins the Tang Clan

70
00:09:18,300 --> 00:09:19,340
Wuning Hall's name.

71
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,350
Who are you?

72
00:09:23,430 --> 00:09:24,010
You

73
00:09:24,530 --> 00:09:25,180
now rank second.

74
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:28,930
The other two rank too low,

75
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:29,940
I can't remember them.

76
00:09:30,070 --> 00:09:31,770
Who can see the Dragon-Tiger List,

77
00:09:32,330 --> 00:09:33,510
you should know that well.

78
00:09:33,830 --> 00:09:34,770
Since you're

79
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:35,770
an ally, not an enemy,

80
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:36,910
do us a favor.

81
00:09:37,160 --> 00:09:38,210
Don't interfere with us

82
00:09:38,330 --> 00:09:39,410
reclaiming Tang Clan property.

83
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:40,740
Tang Clan property?

84
00:09:41,330 --> 00:09:42,440
If it belongs to the Tang Clan,

85
00:09:42,730 --> 00:09:44,210
then why was it with Shengyun Manor?

86
00:09:44,360 --> 00:09:45,620
I'm sure you know

87
00:09:45,730 --> 00:09:46,810
the Tang Clan and Shengyun Manor

88
00:09:46,930 --> 00:09:47,710
have long been enemies.

89
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:48,700
What happened today,

90
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,620
the reasons behind it

91
00:09:49,660 --> 00:09:50,770
is not for outsiders to know.

92
00:09:52,430 --> 00:09:53,670
Then what does

93
00:09:53,680 --> 00:09:54,500
this Tang Clan item look like?

94
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:55,400
Any markings?

95
00:09:55,420 --> 00:09:56,140
Let me hear it.

96
00:09:57,390 --> 00:09:59,240
Don't tell me you don't even know that

97
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:00,610
and still came out on this job.

98
00:10:03,060 --> 00:10:03,440
It's fine.

99
00:10:03,470 --> 00:10:04,870
If you keep meddling in this,

100
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,110
the entire Tang Clan

101
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,410
will make sure

102
00:10:07,530 --> 00:10:08,370
you never know peace again.

103
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,390
Then ask Tang Tianhao

104
00:10:14,390 --> 00:10:15,150
if he dares.

105
00:10:15,390 --> 00:10:16,290
He's never

106
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:17,810
spoken to me like that.

107
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:19,520
If you ask me,

108
00:10:19,730 --> 00:10:21,150
this thing was never

109
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,310
from the Tang Clan.

110
00:10:22,500 --> 00:10:23,590
That's why you can't say

111
00:10:23,590 --> 00:10:24,140
what it is.

112
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,010
Or maybe

113
00:10:25,530 --> 00:10:26,980
it's something you can't

114
00:10:27,860 --> 00:10:29,600
let others know about.

115
00:10:30,460 --> 00:10:31,940
You really want to know?

116
00:10:41,830 --> 00:10:42,770
Only...

117
00:10:43,260 --> 00:10:44,580
once you know,

118
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:46,370
there's no living after that!

119
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:51,870
These must be

120
00:10:51,870 --> 00:10:53,110
the head of Shengyun Manor,

121
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,140
Jiao Chaogui

122
00:10:54,140 --> 00:10:55,260
[Jiao Chaogui, Shengyun Manor's Master]

123
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:56,720
and Second Master Mu Xiuquan.

124
00:10:56,790 --> 00:10:57,670
[Mu Xiuquan]
Who killed

125
00:10:57,760 --> 00:10:58,340
[Shengyun Manor's Second Master]
Ge Yunfei?

126
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,310
That had nothing to do with us.

127
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:02,660
Your Third Master's death

128
00:11:02,880 --> 00:11:04,240
and where that thing went...

129
00:11:04,600 --> 00:11:05,610
those three know best.

130
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,840
What rotten luck today.

131
00:12:03,790 --> 00:12:04,710
Seriously?

132
00:12:05,060 --> 00:12:06,020
Shengyun Manor

133
00:12:06,020 --> 00:12:07,560
has suffered so much from Tang Clan.

134
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:09,310
Why are they still so reckless?

135
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:29,560
Don't misunderstand.

136
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,640
I know the rules,

137
00:12:31,840 --> 00:12:32,910
I don't side with anyone.

138
00:12:33,160 --> 00:12:33,810
Sorry about that,

139
00:12:33,930 --> 00:12:34,510
please continue.

140
00:12:45,630 --> 00:12:47,340
I already apologized just now.

141
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,600
Why won't you let it go?

142
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:49,180
Do you really want me dead?

143
00:12:49,250 --> 00:12:50,110
How is that possible?

144
00:12:50,280 --> 00:12:51,670
Cushion Palm blocks all weapons.

145
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:54,570
Something's off here.

146
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:55,110
Let's go first!

147
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:04,070
You're from Linglong Manor?

148
00:13:05,550 --> 00:13:06,940
Since you're a friend of the Huo family,

149
00:13:07,030 --> 00:13:08,810
thank you for helping us.

150
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,660
We'll take the child now.

151
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:11,520
No need to thank me.

152
00:13:11,650 --> 00:13:12,610
What I did just now

153
00:13:12,610 --> 00:13:13,590
wasn't to help you.

154
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,120
This child

155
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,400
isn't from Shengyun Manor.

156
00:13:16,680 --> 00:13:17,780
You can't take him away.

157
00:13:19,000 --> 00:13:21,110
Since you insist on meddling,

158
00:13:21,560 --> 00:13:22,240
I

159
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:23,940
can only offend the Huo family!

160
00:14:10,610 --> 00:14:12,160
This score between you and Tang Clan...

161
00:14:12,530 --> 00:14:13,170
I

162
00:14:13,270 --> 00:14:14,700
will settle it with you another day!

163
00:14:35,060 --> 00:14:35,910
Where are you going?

164
00:14:41,730 --> 00:14:42,710
Xiangyang?

165
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,340
I'll take you there.

166
00:14:49,560 --> 00:14:50,640
You don't want an escort?

167
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:53,840
But I really did

168
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:55,410
get myself into big trouble.

169
00:14:55,790 --> 00:14:57,580
I'm afraid if I go to Xiangyang with you,

170
00:14:57,730 --> 00:14:58,540
I'll drag you into it.

171
00:15:05,420 --> 00:15:06,160
Wait!

172
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,410
I'd better take you there,

173
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:10,490
it's too dangerous.

174
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,310
Your clothes are covered in blood,

175
00:15:12,860 --> 00:15:13,540
you'll be too noticeable out there.

176
00:15:14,130 --> 00:15:14,810
Wait here a second,

177
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,410
I'll get you some clean clothes.

178
00:15:17,930 --> 00:15:18,770
Wait for me,

179
00:15:19,740 --> 00:15:20,740
I'll be right back.

180
00:15:22,350 --> 00:15:23,240
Don't leave.

181
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,300
These pants

182
00:15:31,300 --> 00:15:32,370
might be a little long on you,

183
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:32,810
but...

184
00:15:36,070 --> 00:15:36,610
Where'd he go?

185
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:22,300
[Feng Shao, Xiangzhou Military Envoy]

186
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:23,850
You ran the moment you saw the officers.

187
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,580
You're definitely hiding something.

188
00:16:25,990 --> 00:16:26,850
Take him back.

189
00:16:27,160 --> 00:16:28,210
We'll question him slowly.

190
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:36,140
Cai!

191
00:16:36,230 --> 00:16:37,340
Boil me ginger soup and hot water!

192
00:16:44,790 --> 00:16:45,110
Go.

193
00:16:52,590 --> 00:16:53,190
Cai!

194
00:16:53,380 --> 00:16:53,830
Get out here!

195
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:54,860
Envoy Feng!

196
00:16:55,920 --> 00:16:56,500
Envoy Feng!

197
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:58,030
Thank goodness you're here!

198
00:16:58,040 --> 00:16:58,810
If you hadn't shown up soon,

199
00:16:58,810 --> 00:16:59,860
I would've gone to the authorities too.

200
00:17:00,550 --> 00:17:01,290
What happened here?

201
00:17:01,450 --> 00:17:02,330
Why are there so many dead people here?

202
00:17:03,250 --> 00:17:04,290
Don't just look out here,

203
00:17:04,290 --> 00:17:06,260
there's one nailed up inside too.

204
00:17:12,580 --> 00:17:14,430
Envoy Feng, look.

205
00:17:15,030 --> 00:17:15,590
Look.

206
00:17:22,050 --> 00:17:22,830
Who did this?

207
00:17:23,090 --> 00:17:23,830
No idea.

208
00:17:25,980 --> 00:17:26,900
What about the four outside?

209
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:27,760
Never seen them.

210
00:17:28,650 --> 00:17:30,060
Are you messing with me?

211
00:17:30,150 --> 00:17:30,900
I wouldn't dare.

212
00:17:30,980 --> 00:17:31,960
The one outside...

213
00:17:32,120 --> 00:17:33,060
Three men in black killed him,

214
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:34,260
and they ran right after.

215
00:17:34,650 --> 00:17:35,960
I don't know who they were.

216
00:17:36,180 --> 00:17:36,720
As for this one,

217
00:17:36,720 --> 00:17:37,400
I have no idea

218
00:17:37,400 --> 00:17:38,260
how he died.

219
00:17:38,450 --> 00:17:39,530
From what you're saying,

220
00:17:39,650 --> 00:17:40,620
the killer probably

221
00:17:40,620 --> 00:17:41,940
isn't the one we're after.

222
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:42,890
Go send word.

223
00:17:52,710 --> 00:17:53,300
Envoy Feng,

224
00:17:53,380 --> 00:17:54,930
who did you signal just now?

225
00:17:55,080 --> 00:17:56,730
If more honored guests are coming,

226
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:58,830
my inn can prepare for them.

227
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:00,430
Who?

228
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:03,560
Of course my superior.

229
00:18:03,780 --> 00:18:04,900
Our Xiangzhou Prefecture's

230
00:18:05,050 --> 00:18:06,300
Cavalry Commander,

231
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:08,060
Lord Shao Jizu.

232
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:23,460
[Yicheng County Border]

233
00:18:36,750 --> 00:18:37,250
Commander Shao.

234
00:18:38,180 --> 00:18:39,350
[Shao Jizu, Xiangzhou Cavalry Commander]

235
00:18:39,350 --> 00:18:40,360
Found the suspect?

236
00:18:41,580 --> 00:18:42,860
Not sure he's the suspect,

237
00:18:43,180 --> 00:18:44,760
but I found something strange.

238
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:57,060
These people clearly had

239
00:18:57,070 --> 00:18:59,040
blade wounds, not sword wounds.

240
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:01,110
And they died from poison.

241
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:03,490
Obviously the Tang Clan's work.

242
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,780
Could you not tell,

243
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:09,160
or did you not even check?

244
00:19:09,510 --> 00:19:10,830
What I don't understand is

245
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,490
why Tang Clan was here.

246
00:19:13,080 --> 00:19:13,760
Could it be

247
00:19:13,950 --> 00:19:15,100
they were after that person too?

248
00:19:15,780 --> 00:19:17,600
The master has other plans for them.

249
00:19:20,080 --> 00:19:20,690
Inside,

250
00:19:21,120 --> 00:19:21,860
there's another corpse.

251
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:39,140
Search this place

252
00:19:39,140 --> 00:19:40,560
inside and out.

253
00:19:40,750 --> 00:19:42,030
Don't miss a single corner.

254
00:19:42,080 --> 00:19:42,600
Yes, sir!

255
00:20:30,880 --> 00:20:31,460
Be careful.

256
00:20:31,580 --> 00:20:32,130
Don't make a sound.

257
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,690
Who are you?

258
00:20:45,370 --> 00:20:45,970
Watch out!

259
00:20:48,650 --> 00:20:49,700
Was it you

260
00:20:49,700 --> 00:20:51,100
who blocked Ge Yunfei's flying halberd?

261
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:51,900
Cai,

262
00:20:51,980 --> 00:20:53,330
you sure no one's hiding here?

263
00:20:53,850 --> 00:20:54,330
Envoy Feng,

264
00:20:54,450 --> 00:20:56,100
I only have a few guest rooms.

265
00:20:56,180 --> 00:20:57,360
There's nowhere to hide.

266
00:20:57,710 --> 00:20:58,760
Commander Shao said it himself:

267
00:20:59,050 --> 00:21:00,360
not a single corner gets missed.

268
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:02,230
If we find something,

269
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:03,780
you'll never cover for it.

270
00:21:09,050 --> 00:21:09,460
Envoy Feng,

271
00:21:10,600 --> 00:21:11,800
that's Lord Shao?

272
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:13,530
He's so young,

273
00:21:13,880 --> 00:21:14,900
and quite handsome too.

274
00:21:15,380 --> 00:21:16,160
So impressive.

275
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:16,830
Of course.

276
00:21:17,980 --> 00:21:19,530
Everything's peaceful around Xiangzhou

277
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:20,490
because of him.

278
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:21,830
His reputation keeps order.

279
00:21:22,680 --> 00:21:24,160
Even the Prince of Xiangyang

280
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:25,730
thinks highly of him.

281
00:21:26,850 --> 00:21:28,450
He's even arranging a marriage between Lord Shao

282
00:21:28,450 --> 00:21:29,760
and Linglong Manor's eldest daughter.

283
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:32,060
They'll be married very soon.

284
00:21:36,650 --> 00:21:37,260
Commander Shao.

285
00:21:37,350 --> 00:21:38,230
Anything suspicious?

286
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:39,300
We searched everywhere. Nothing.

287
00:21:40,120 --> 00:21:41,160
Did you search the yard too?

288
00:21:41,280 --> 00:21:41,690
Yes.

289
00:21:46,410 --> 00:21:47,220
Take a look.

290
00:21:48,150 --> 00:21:49,260
Have you seen this man?

291
00:21:51,080 --> 00:21:51,750
No.

292
00:21:52,580 --> 00:21:53,830
Look carefully.

293
00:22:00,250 --> 00:22:00,760
Commander Shao,

294
00:22:01,450 --> 00:22:02,260
I think I have.

295
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,520
When?

296
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:05,160
I can't quite remember.

297
00:22:05,320 --> 00:22:06,960
I think it was a day or two ago.

298
00:22:07,250 --> 00:22:09,280
That was before the killings outside,

299
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:10,130
he already left.

300
00:22:10,950 --> 00:22:12,060
Which way did he go?
(Watch on www,kisskh,la to support Admin)

301
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:13,730
I really don't know.

302
00:22:16,250 --> 00:22:17,300
Then think carefully

303
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:19,260
over the next couple days.

304
00:22:19,480 --> 00:22:20,430
If you remember anything,

305
00:22:20,510 --> 00:22:21,430
come find me.

306
00:22:21,510 --> 00:22:22,730
You'll be well rewarded.

307
00:22:23,080 --> 00:22:24,060
Of course.

308
00:22:24,950 --> 00:22:26,460
May I ask something?

309
00:22:26,550 --> 00:22:28,060
Who exactly is this man?

310
00:22:28,180 --> 00:22:29,000
Why would the authorities

311
00:22:29,000 --> 00:22:30,160
send so many men after him?

312
00:22:30,350 --> 00:22:32,270
He looks pretty refined.

313
00:22:32,320 --> 00:22:34,230
He's even more dangerous than the killer

314
00:22:34,250 --> 00:22:35,030
of those five people?

315
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,660
This man kills without mercy.

316
00:22:37,050 --> 00:22:38,230
Five people?

317
00:22:38,440 --> 00:22:40,130
He's killed fifty before.

318
00:22:40,710 --> 00:22:41,430
So...

319
00:22:41,950 --> 00:22:43,960
don't let his face fool you.

320
00:22:45,350 --> 00:22:46,260
Commander Shao, don't worry.

321
00:22:46,980 --> 00:22:47,690
If I see him,

322
00:22:47,780 --> 00:22:48,430
I'll report it immediately.

323
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,030
He won't get away.

324
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:06,960
Forgive my poor judgment,

325
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:08,560
could this man

326
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,100
not have died by Tang Clan's hand?

327
00:23:10,550 --> 00:23:11,630
The fatal wound

328
00:23:12,280 --> 00:23:13,660
was of course Tang Clan poison.

329
00:23:14,680 --> 00:23:15,930
But the interesting part

330
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:18,660
is the broken halberd in his chest.

331
00:23:40,450 --> 00:23:41,230
Wait.

332
00:24:05,550 --> 00:24:06,130
Could it be

333
00:24:06,250 --> 00:24:06,900
this sword

334
00:24:07,680 --> 00:24:09,300
was broken by that halberd?

335
00:24:10,250 --> 00:24:10,900
Innkeeper.

336
00:24:11,780 --> 00:24:12,300
Yes, sir?

337
00:24:14,510 --> 00:24:15,860
Whose sword is this?

338
00:24:16,680 --> 00:24:17,430
At the time,

339
00:24:17,580 --> 00:24:19,060
they called him Lord Jiao.

340
00:24:22,650 --> 00:24:24,260
This man

341
00:24:24,450 --> 00:24:25,730
threw the halberd

342
00:24:26,480 --> 00:24:28,460
and struck Jiao Chaogui's sword.

343
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:30,300
The impact changed its direction

344
00:24:30,980 --> 00:24:32,430
and hit Mu Xiuquan.

345
00:24:32,850 --> 00:24:34,690
To pull off such a precise strike,

346
00:24:34,770 --> 00:24:36,560
his martial arts must be unmatched.

347
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:39,190
If his skills

348
00:24:39,190 --> 00:24:40,550
really are that incredible,

349
00:24:43,380 --> 00:24:45,490
then why not kill them directly?

350
00:24:47,400 --> 00:24:49,220
Why borrow force against force

351
00:24:49,220 --> 00:24:50,960
and rely on finesse instead?

352
00:24:51,450 --> 00:24:52,260
Could it be...

353
00:24:52,970 --> 00:24:54,090
This man wanted to hide

354
00:24:54,090 --> 00:24:55,460
his martial arts style?

355
00:24:57,150 --> 00:24:58,060
There's another possibility.

356
00:24:59,580 --> 00:25:01,900
He can no longer use stronger moves,

357
00:25:02,980 --> 00:25:04,430
so he relies on skill alone.

358
00:25:09,380 --> 00:25:10,830
To leave Xiangzhou,

359
00:25:11,180 --> 00:25:12,350
there are only three waterways

360
00:25:12,350 --> 00:25:13,290
and two land routes.

361
00:25:14,180 --> 00:25:16,070
Have the prefecture issue strict orders.

362
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:17,470
Guard every ferry crossing,

363
00:25:17,470 --> 00:25:18,200
post station,

364
00:25:18,320 --> 00:25:19,680
and shut down the horse markets too.

365
00:25:19,680 --> 00:25:20,830
As long as we secure

366
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:22,130
every checkpoint

367
00:25:22,280 --> 00:25:23,840
and inspect every traveler,

368
00:25:24,090 --> 00:25:25,220
even if he wants to escape,

369
00:25:25,580 --> 00:25:27,100
he won't get far.

370
00:25:28,120 --> 00:25:29,100
You little brat, Shao,

371
00:25:29,980 --> 00:25:30,660
so ruthless.

372
00:25:37,980 --> 00:25:38,830
They're gone.

373
00:25:45,050 --> 00:25:45,560
Wait.

374
00:25:47,080 --> 00:25:47,940
Who are you exactly?

375
00:25:48,540 --> 00:25:49,580
I'm nobody important.

376
00:25:50,200 --> 00:25:51,870
My name isn't worth mentioning.

377
00:25:52,450 --> 00:25:53,630
You're hiding here,

378
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,230
so who are you hiding from?

379
00:25:55,510 --> 00:25:57,430
Wielding the legendary Yinyang An,

380
00:25:57,620 --> 00:25:58,750
with the "Glimpse of Beauty" technique

381
00:25:58,750 --> 00:25:59,690
mastered to perfection,

382
00:25:59,780 --> 00:26:01,900
and the secret art of hearing voices

383
00:26:02,370 --> 00:26:03,990
from a hundred paces away.

384
00:26:04,180 --> 00:26:05,260
I assume you're

385
00:26:05,450 --> 00:26:06,730
from Linglong Manor.

386
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:09,160
You recognized my movement technique?

387
00:26:13,250 --> 00:26:13,830
Wait.

388
00:26:14,280 --> 00:26:15,300
How do you know Yinyang An?

389
00:26:17,280 --> 00:26:17,930
I've been drifting around for years.

390
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:19,860
So naturally,

391
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,160
I know a few old tales.

392
00:26:21,380 --> 00:26:21,930
Legend says

393
00:26:22,280 --> 00:26:23,560
Yinyang An was forged with Blackfire

394
00:26:23,920 --> 00:26:25,160
to counter yin-based martial arts.

395
00:26:25,550 --> 00:26:26,800
Wuning Hall's Cushion Palm

396
00:26:26,850 --> 00:26:28,630
could withstand Jiao Chaogui and others' swords,

397
00:26:28,750 --> 00:26:30,150
yet you pierced straight through his palm.

398
00:26:30,320 --> 00:26:31,030
A weapon like this

399
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:33,130
truly lives up to its legend.

400
00:26:34,750 --> 00:26:36,060
At least you've got some taste.

401
00:26:36,180 --> 00:26:37,490
Since you've figured it out,

402
00:26:37,580 --> 00:26:38,830
I've got nothing to hide.

403
00:26:39,510 --> 00:26:40,060
Yes,

404
00:26:40,350 --> 00:26:41,960
I am from Linglong Manor.

405
00:26:42,120 --> 00:26:43,230
My name is Huo Xiaodi,

406
00:26:43,710 --> 00:26:44,740
[Huo Xiaodi]
the lowest-ranked disciple

407
00:26:44,740 --> 00:26:45,580
[Disciple of Linglong Manor]
from Linglong Manor.

408
00:26:47,550 --> 00:26:48,130
Looks like

409
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:50,560
Linglong Manor's standing

410
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:52,100
runs deeper than I thought.

411
00:26:53,120 --> 00:26:54,260
Even a low-ranked disciple

412
00:26:54,380 --> 00:26:55,860
can casually name Tang Clan's heir

413
00:26:56,120 --> 00:26:57,660
and prefecture commanders.

414
00:26:59,320 --> 00:27:01,060
Stop changing the subject.

415
00:27:02,650 --> 00:27:04,130
I already told you my name.

416
00:27:04,280 --> 00:27:05,100
Now it's your turn.

417
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:15,230
My surname is Zhan.

418
00:27:15,230 --> 00:27:15,750
[Zhan Rifei]

419
00:27:15,750 --> 00:27:16,490
[Martial Wanderer]
Given name is Rifei.

420
00:27:20,920 --> 00:27:21,770
That sword of yours

421
00:27:21,770 --> 00:27:22,760
doesn't look ordinary either.

422
00:27:25,850 --> 00:27:26,490
You know it?

423
00:27:27,320 --> 00:27:28,860
If I'm not mistaken,

424
00:27:31,650 --> 00:27:33,330
this was forged by Tang Dynasty swordsmith

425
00:27:33,330 --> 00:27:34,350
Zhang Yajiu.

426
00:27:34,560 --> 00:27:35,490
It's called Yanling.

427
00:27:40,710 --> 00:27:42,900
Linglong Manor may have quite a reputation,

428
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:45,060
but few people know

429
00:27:45,550 --> 00:27:46,750
the Huo family ancestors

430
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:47,730
were swordsmiths.

431
00:27:47,980 --> 00:27:49,960
They built their fortune through forging.

432
00:27:50,120 --> 00:27:51,460
They're well versed in weapons.

433
00:27:52,180 --> 00:27:53,480
In the manor library,

434
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:54,490
there are countless ancient texts.

435
00:27:54,490 --> 00:27:55,570
I've loved reading them since childhood.

436
00:27:55,570 --> 00:27:56,900
All the famous weapons

437
00:27:56,900 --> 00:27:58,090
are already memorized by heart.

438
00:28:01,810 --> 00:28:03,530
Your Yanling Sword is easy to spot.

439
00:28:04,140 --> 00:28:05,130
It's two inches longer

440
00:28:05,280 --> 00:28:06,740
and twice as heavy as normal swords.

441
00:28:06,750 --> 00:28:07,430
And the inscription

442
00:28:07,430 --> 00:28:08,520
isn't carved on the hilt,

443
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:09,860
[Yanling]
it's carved on the blade itself.

444
00:28:12,050 --> 00:28:12,760
You're impressive.

445
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,660
I've learned something new again.

446
00:28:15,140 --> 00:28:16,140
I also know

447
00:28:17,710 --> 00:28:18,660
this sword

448
00:28:18,900 --> 00:28:20,130
isn't your usual weapon.

449
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:22,660
With skills like yours,

450
00:28:23,250 --> 00:28:25,310
you must be someone well-known.

451
00:28:27,050 --> 00:28:28,950
Using such an obscure sword

452
00:28:29,580 --> 00:28:31,100
is to hide your identity.

453
00:28:33,920 --> 00:28:35,100
I thought we agreed

454
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:37,260
not to ask about each other's identities.

455
00:28:38,510 --> 00:28:38,960
Fine.

456
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:41,330
You don't have to tell me your real name,

457
00:28:41,330 --> 00:28:42,790
then tell me why you're hiding.

458
00:28:43,750 --> 00:28:44,830
And why are you hiding?

459
00:28:45,550 --> 00:28:46,490
From Shao Jizu.

460
00:28:47,390 --> 00:28:48,080
You mean

461
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:49,030
those officers earlier

462
00:28:49,030 --> 00:28:50,030
were after you?

463
00:28:51,580 --> 00:28:53,030
Then what crime did you commit?

464
00:28:53,350 --> 00:28:54,330
I didn't commit any crime.

465
00:28:56,120 --> 00:28:57,320
It's Shao Jizu.

466
00:28:57,680 --> 00:28:58,560
He's abusing his power

467
00:28:58,710 --> 00:29:00,480
using a manhunt as an excuse to chase me.

468
00:29:00,980 --> 00:29:02,830
He's showing my portrait everywhere too.

469
00:29:03,180 --> 00:29:04,930
The portrait he had was yours?

470
00:29:06,380 --> 00:29:07,610
He even called me

471
00:29:07,610 --> 00:29:08,930
a bloodthirsty demon.

472
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:11,340
For personal revenge,

473
00:29:11,340 --> 00:29:12,690
who knows what else he'll do.

474
00:29:12,980 --> 00:29:14,230
You have a grudge against him?

475
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:19,560
Forget it. Never mind.

476
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:24,160
I heard Lord Shao

477
00:29:24,450 --> 00:29:25,910
is engaged to Huo daughter.

478
00:29:26,120 --> 00:29:27,230
He's treating you like this,

479
00:29:27,480 --> 00:29:29,000
and he's not afraid of offending Linglong Manor?

480
00:29:29,140 --> 00:29:30,100
What engagement?

481
00:29:30,100 --> 00:29:30,690
Nonsense.

482
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:32,690
Our young mistress isn't engaged to him.

483
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:38,300
The Prince of Xiangyang arranged it.

484
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:39,300
How could that be fake?

485
00:29:40,680 --> 00:29:41,760
What arranged marriage?

486
00:29:41,880 --> 00:29:42,760
Who arranged it?

487
00:29:42,950 --> 00:29:44,300
Even if the Emperor himself stepped in,

488
00:29:44,380 --> 00:29:45,330
it still wouldn't count.

489
00:29:50,250 --> 00:29:51,260
I was the one asking questions.

490
00:29:51,260 --> 00:29:52,200
How did you turn it around on me again?

491
00:29:54,980 --> 00:29:56,300
I am hiding from an enemy,

492
00:29:57,350 --> 00:29:58,900
but I can't reveal who it is.

493
00:29:59,650 --> 00:30:00,490
I'm afraid

494
00:30:00,650 --> 00:30:01,660
I'd bring trouble upon you.

495
00:30:04,650 --> 00:30:06,950
I think you're just bluffing.

496
00:30:07,510 --> 00:30:08,970
In Xiangzhou Prefecture,

497
00:30:08,970 --> 00:30:10,230
who would dare provoke the Huo family?

498
00:30:11,850 --> 00:30:13,220
Since the Huo family

499
00:30:13,220 --> 00:30:14,100
cannot be challenged here,

500
00:30:14,710 --> 00:30:15,960
when you get into trouble,

501
00:30:16,680 --> 00:30:18,060
why not reveal your identity?

502
00:30:22,880 --> 00:30:24,030
I won't ask you, so don't ask me.

503
00:30:43,125 --> 00:30:48,125
(Watch on www.kisskh.xyz Support Admin)

504
00:30:45,150 --> 00:30:45,730
Innkeeper,

505
00:30:46,550 --> 00:30:48,030
where's the boy tied up earlier?

506
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:49,260
They took him away.

507
00:30:49,550 --> 00:30:50,430
Where to?

508
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:52,330
I heard they brought him to town

509
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:53,690
and handed him to the local authorities.

510
00:30:56,250 --> 00:30:57,430
They ignore murder cases

511
00:30:57,780 --> 00:30:59,060
and go after a little boy instead.

512
00:30:59,350 --> 00:31:00,900
So that's how these officers work.

513
00:31:01,550 --> 00:31:03,430
You're clearly not from around here.

514
00:31:03,780 --> 00:31:05,160
Things in Xiangzhou

515
00:31:05,280 --> 00:31:06,730
have always been this way.

516
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:08,060
My inn

517
00:31:08,060 --> 00:31:09,340
can't even make a dime.

518
00:31:09,340 --> 00:31:10,260
Every day it's just

519
00:31:10,300 --> 00:31:11,900
carrying corpses and burying bodies.

520
00:31:12,850 --> 00:31:14,900
Why run this inn anymore?

521
00:31:15,050 --> 00:31:16,230
I'm done with it.

522
00:31:16,680 --> 00:31:17,260
I'm quitting.

523
00:31:18,750 --> 00:31:20,020
I'm selling coffins instead!

524
00:31:20,020 --> 00:31:20,830
Selling coffins!

525
00:31:21,150 --> 00:31:22,160
I'll sell coffins...

526
00:31:27,580 --> 00:31:28,900
Thanks for earlier.

527
00:31:30,920 --> 00:31:31,760
You're truly my savior!

528
00:31:32,510 --> 00:31:33,300
Safe travels!

529
00:31:35,180 --> 00:31:36,100
Where are you going?

530
00:31:36,320 --> 00:31:37,160
We can travel together.

531
00:31:38,050 --> 00:31:39,060
I've already got trouble on my back,

532
00:31:39,580 --> 00:31:40,930
I shouldn't travel with you.

533
00:31:41,320 --> 00:31:42,680
I think you're afraid of getting involved

534
00:31:42,680 --> 00:31:43,690
with Shao Jizu because of me.

535
00:31:44,910 --> 00:31:45,840
Your martial arts are amazing.

536
00:31:45,840 --> 00:31:46,490
What is there to fear?

537
00:31:47,300 --> 00:31:47,690
No.

538
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:49,140
That can't be it.

539
00:31:49,580 --> 00:31:50,270
Otherwise you wouldn't

540
00:31:50,270 --> 00:31:51,590
risk exposing yourself

541
00:31:51,590 --> 00:31:52,560
just to help me out.

542
00:31:53,150 --> 00:31:53,960
I still haven't thanked you.

543
00:31:56,150 --> 00:31:57,100
You're the same, Huo.

544
00:31:57,780 --> 00:31:58,560
You were clearly fleeing,

545
00:31:59,050 --> 00:31:59,900
yet you still stepped in

546
00:31:59,980 --> 00:32:00,830
to save that boy.

547
00:32:01,680 --> 00:32:03,060
That's true heroism.

548
00:32:03,180 --> 00:32:04,030
If you keep thanking me,

549
00:32:04,150 --> 00:32:04,760
it'll sound too formal.

550
00:32:07,750 --> 00:32:09,560
So how long have you trained?

551
00:32:09,980 --> 00:32:11,260
Even Shao Jizu admires your skills.

552
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,590
He even thought

553
00:32:12,590 --> 00:32:13,490
I was behind all that.

554
00:32:13,680 --> 00:32:15,270
If I had your skills,

555
00:32:15,270 --> 00:32:16,470
I'd have wiped out

556
00:32:16,470 --> 00:32:17,300
every villain out there by now.

557
00:32:20,320 --> 00:32:21,210
Which way are you headed?

558
00:32:22,250 --> 00:32:22,830
Back to the capital.

559
00:32:23,350 --> 00:32:24,360
I just asked around,

560
00:32:24,650 --> 00:32:26,460
the boy was taken by the authorities.

561
00:32:26,750 --> 00:32:27,860
We can save him together

562
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:28,760
and head north after.

563
00:32:33,480 --> 00:32:34,560
I have too many enemies,

564
00:32:34,710 --> 00:32:35,900
I'd rather not drag you down.

565
00:32:36,120 --> 00:32:36,890
Shao Jizu

566
00:32:36,890 --> 00:32:38,410
isn't traveling with his men.

567
00:32:38,510 --> 00:32:39,630
With your skills,

568
00:32:39,750 --> 00:32:41,060
those useless officers

569
00:32:41,350 --> 00:32:42,130
are no match for you.

570
00:32:43,380 --> 00:32:43,730
Alright.

571
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:46,160
I can't force you into it.

572
00:32:47,180 --> 00:32:48,030
Then farewell.

573
00:32:52,650 --> 00:32:53,260
Wait.

574
00:32:54,550 --> 00:32:55,430
You changed your mind?

575
00:32:58,180 --> 00:32:59,100
That boy

576
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:00,460
is the only survivor today.

577
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:02,430
Maybe only he knows

578
00:33:02,510 --> 00:33:03,360
where the treasure Tang Clan

579
00:33:03,390 --> 00:33:04,660
and Shengyun Manor fought over is.

580
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:06,490
After you save him,

581
00:33:06,580 --> 00:33:08,060
those two factions won't stop chasing you.

582
00:33:08,550 --> 00:33:09,460
Be careful.

583
00:33:11,780 --> 00:33:12,260
I know.

584
00:33:13,840 --> 00:33:15,730
I just can't stand by

585
00:33:15,730 --> 00:33:17,200
and watch him fall into danger again.

586
00:33:19,140 --> 00:33:20,560
But I'll remember your warning.

587
00:33:21,120 --> 00:33:22,400
I'm not afraid of Tang Clan.

588
00:33:22,780 --> 00:33:23,990
If their young master found out

589
00:33:23,990 --> 00:33:25,100
his men attacked me,

590
00:33:25,250 --> 00:33:26,230
he'd skin them alive.

591
00:33:26,850 --> 00:33:28,230
As for Shengyun Manor,

592
00:33:28,780 --> 00:33:30,030
if I can't win, I'll run.

593
00:33:33,120 --> 00:33:34,230
Your movement skills are unmatched.

594
00:33:34,710 --> 00:33:35,710
As long as you're careful,

595
00:33:36,450 --> 00:33:37,490
getting away shouldn't be hard.

596
00:33:39,920 --> 00:33:40,900
We'll meet again.

597
00:33:41,950 --> 00:33:42,880
Then I wish you

598
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,900
a swift escape from your troubles.

599
00:33:44,650 --> 00:33:45,860
See you in the capital someday.

600
00:34:06,450 --> 00:34:07,060
Move it!

601
00:34:07,150 --> 00:34:07,990
Quit dragging your feet!

602
00:34:08,650 --> 00:34:09,490
We won't reach town before dark!

603
00:34:19,380 --> 00:34:20,060
You there!

604
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:21,100
Are you blind?

605
00:34:21,380 --> 00:34:22,720
Can't you see officers on duty?

606
00:34:23,110 --> 00:34:23,980
Now get out

607
00:34:24,050 --> 00:34:24,830
of my way!

608
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:29,530
Who are you people?

609
00:34:29,650 --> 00:34:30,490
What do you want?

610
00:34:33,280 --> 00:34:34,860
I want something from you.

611
00:34:35,110 --> 00:34:35,900
What thing?

612
00:34:36,350 --> 00:34:37,360
Your head.

613
00:34:52,080 --> 00:34:53,330
This Zhan Rifei

614
00:34:53,890 --> 00:34:55,720
keeps praising my skills,

615
00:34:55,950 --> 00:34:57,300
but he clearly doesn't mean it.

616
00:34:57,900 --> 00:34:58,750
He's obviously afraid

617
00:34:58,750 --> 00:34:59,630
I'd slow him down.

618
00:34:59,880 --> 00:35:01,030
That's why he refused to travel with me.

619
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:26,020
Everyone in Hanshui Palace

620
00:35:26,020 --> 00:35:27,130
has been punished.

621
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,430
We came this time

622
00:35:36,550 --> 00:35:38,160
specifically to bring you back.

623
00:35:38,380 --> 00:35:39,460
Tell me,

624
00:35:40,150 --> 00:35:41,060
that secret...

625
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:42,760
did you tell anyone else?

626
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:45,860
You may not be able to speak,

627
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,530
but if you wanted to tell someone,

628
00:35:47,680 --> 00:35:48,810
you'd find a way.

629
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:49,690
Right?

630
00:35:51,780 --> 00:35:52,760
You really didn't tell anyone?

631
00:35:55,980 --> 00:35:57,170
People from Hanshui Palace.

632
00:36:04,510 --> 00:36:06,060
It's been a while since your medicine.

633
00:36:07,300 --> 00:36:07,970
This medicine...

634
00:36:08,080 --> 00:36:10,010
It does look like a larger dose today,

635
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,490
it'll just hurt a bit more.

636
00:36:24,930 --> 00:36:25,980
If you still won't drink it,

637
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:28,510
Granny will get angry.

638
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:29,740
You know her.

639
00:36:30,030 --> 00:36:31,300
She has plenty of ways

640
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:32,670
to make you wish you were dead.

641
00:36:37,190 --> 00:36:38,360
If even one drop is missing,

642
00:36:38,360 --> 00:36:39,340
the medicine loses its effect!

643
00:36:39,340 --> 00:36:40,850
You're stalling on purpose!

644
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,240
I'll just make another bowl.

645
00:36:46,760 --> 00:36:47,710
When did you get here?

646
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:48,440
Just arrived.

647
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:49,910
That's impossible.

648
00:36:50,590 --> 00:36:52,040
My hearing technique

649
00:36:52,190 --> 00:36:53,850
lets me hear every movement

650
00:36:53,850 --> 00:36:54,570
within a hundred paces.

651
00:36:55,430 --> 00:36:56,240
You were too focused

652
00:36:56,400 --> 00:36:56,910
and lowered your guard.

653
00:36:57,540 --> 00:36:58,110
I came

654
00:36:58,560 --> 00:36:59,980
to ask you for a favor.

655
00:37:00,430 --> 00:37:01,340
Me?

656
00:37:01,460 --> 00:37:02,340
How can I help you?

657
00:37:02,800 --> 00:37:04,290
There's an annoying pest

658
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:05,310
who won't stop tailing me.

659
00:37:05,920 --> 00:37:07,360
I'd like your help shaking him off.

660
00:37:07,690 --> 00:37:08,880
Who's so capable

661
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:09,620
that even you can't lose him?

662
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:10,940
Yan Ziqing of the Yunying Sect.

663
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:13,840
No wonder.

664
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:16,170
Yan Ziqing's movement skills are incredible.

665
00:37:16,660 --> 00:37:17,780
But with your martial arts,

666
00:37:17,930 --> 00:37:18,640
are you really afraid of him?

667
00:37:19,160 --> 00:37:20,110
No matter how good I am,

668
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:22,440
I can't match your "Glimpse of Beauty."

669
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:23,210
I'd appreciate it.

670
00:37:26,060 --> 00:37:26,410
Alright.

671
00:37:27,160 --> 00:37:28,040
Once I rescue the mute boy,

672
00:37:28,050 --> 00:37:28,540
I'll help you.

673
00:37:30,230 --> 00:37:31,540
You'll deal with that pest for me,

674
00:37:31,730 --> 00:37:33,110
so I can't just sit around.

675
00:37:33,230 --> 00:37:34,010
I'll rescue the mute boy.

676
00:37:34,330 --> 00:37:35,340
That makes us even,

677
00:37:35,460 --> 00:37:36,170
no one owes anyone.

678
00:37:38,330 --> 00:37:39,110
It's a deal.

679
00:37:39,760 --> 00:37:41,040
But the people of Hanshui Palace

680
00:37:41,040 --> 00:37:42,030
use strange martial arts.

681
00:37:42,030 --> 00:37:42,920
Their weapons are unpredictable too,

682
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:43,710
be very careful.

683
00:37:43,860 --> 00:37:44,440
Got it.

684
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:45,660
We'll meet back here after it's done.

685
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:56,240
Who's there?

686
00:37:59,030 --> 00:38:00,440
Using methods like this

687
00:38:00,590 --> 00:38:01,110
against

688
00:38:01,190 --> 00:38:02,340
an unarmed child...

689
00:38:03,860 --> 00:38:05,810
aren't you ashamed of Hanshui Palace?

690
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:09,540
Since you know our reputation,

691
00:38:09,930 --> 00:38:11,110
stay out of this.

692
00:38:12,460 --> 00:38:14,240
A poison that pierces bone and heart...

693
00:38:15,130 --> 00:38:16,240
truly potent medicine.

694
00:38:16,590 --> 00:38:17,710
If you don't want to drink it,

695
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:18,910
then don't.

696
00:38:19,230 --> 00:38:20,570
And don't return to Hanshui Palace either.

697
00:38:24,130 --> 00:38:25,170
Everlasting Longing.

698
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:26,380
Miss...

699
00:38:26,800 --> 00:38:27,780
are you the Moon Envoy?

700
00:38:27,780 --> 00:38:29,590
[Moon Envoy, Hanshui Palace]

701
00:38:29,590 --> 00:38:30,810
Longing leaves no trace, yet cuts to the bone.

702
00:38:31,060 --> 00:38:32,440
You still have time to leave.

703
00:38:35,430 --> 00:38:37,440
This gentleman carrying the Rainbow-Piercing Sun Saber...

704
00:38:38,160 --> 00:38:39,040
Then you must be the Sun Envoy.

705
00:38:39,140 --> 00:38:40,380
[Sun Envoy, Hanshui Palace]

706
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,410
The two of you

707
00:38:41,960 --> 00:38:43,040
aren't coming at me together?

708
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:44,040
I alone am enough!

709
00:39:24,330 --> 00:39:25,310
No matter how sharp the sword,

710
00:39:25,400 --> 00:39:26,740
it cannot cut through Everlasting Longing.

711
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:28,340
Moon Envoy truly lives up to your name.

712
00:40:39,630 --> 00:40:40,910
You're already badly injured.

713
00:40:41,930 --> 00:40:43,080
In that case,

714
00:40:43,730 --> 00:40:45,160
I'm afraid you won't

715
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:47,340
make it out alive today.

716
00:40:49,660 --> 00:40:50,860
We're no match for him.

717
00:40:52,460 --> 00:40:53,100
Ridiculous.

718
00:40:53,730 --> 00:40:55,000
A dying man

719
00:40:55,330 --> 00:40:56,670
can't be that powerful.

720
00:40:57,970 --> 00:41:01,360
I only need one move to kill.

721
00:42:06,860 --> 00:42:08,480
You're severely injured,

722
00:42:09,130 --> 00:42:10,240
yet you still dared

723
00:42:10,240 --> 00:42:11,810
to take my Thousand-Fold Dragon-Slaying Twist.

724
00:42:12,830 --> 00:42:14,170
Even injured,

725
00:42:15,400 --> 00:42:16,710
I can still defeat you.

726
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,570
You can try

727
00:42:20,800 --> 00:42:22,810
and see if you can use another move.

728
00:42:35,530 --> 00:42:36,910
He's carrying multiple severe injuries.

729
00:42:37,130 --> 00:42:38,140
He won't last much longer.

730
00:42:38,460 --> 00:42:39,570
If we join forces now,

731
00:42:40,060 --> 00:42:41,240
we can definitely kill him.

732
00:42:44,330 --> 00:42:45,140
Even so,

733
00:42:45,460 --> 00:42:46,610
I still see no chance of winning.

734
00:42:48,860 --> 00:42:50,140
We'll meet again.

735
00:43:30,860 --> 00:43:36,340
♪In this martial world, true friends are rare♪

736
00:43:37,020 --> 00:43:41,740
♪Yet some would fight by my side♪

737
00:43:41,900 --> 00:43:43,900
♪Across towering mountains♪

738
00:43:43,940 --> 00:43:48,940
♪Risking all for peace beneath the heavens♪

739
00:43:49,820 --> 00:43:56,220
♪If we face life and death together, why fear the hard road ahead?♪

740
00:43:56,300 --> 00:44:02,780
♪Roaming this endless martial road♪

741
00:44:02,940 --> 00:44:09,180
♪Seeing the world's joy and sorrow pass by♪

742
00:44:09,380 --> 00:44:12,420
♪Honor still burns within us♪

743
00:44:12,540 --> 00:44:18,620
♪Still, love and grudges are the hardest to escape♪

744
00:44:18,860 --> 00:44:23,300
♪Too tangled to let go♪

745
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:29,060
♪Who says loyalty and honor can't coexist?♪

746
00:44:29,060 --> 00:44:32,740
♪One swing of the sword ends it all♪

747
00:44:33,060 --> 00:44:38,660
♪My heart stays true, just as before♪

748
00:44:39,260 --> 00:44:44,380
♪Right and wrong will reveal themselves♪

749
00:44:44,740 --> 00:44:49,620
♪Why let others decide for us?♪

750
00:44:49,860 --> 00:44:54,060
♪If this journey has no way back♪

751
00:44:54,260 --> 00:44:57,660
♪Then there's no need for sorrow♪

752
00:44:58,460 --> 00:45:04,420
♪Let a lone boat carry me past the mountains♪

753
00:45:04,860 --> 00:45:10,100
♪One last glance, and the clouds are gone♪

754
00:45:10,100 --> 00:45:15,700
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪

755
00:45:16,380 --> 00:45:23,180
♪The bright moon will light my way home♪
